title: [Solindago Anox]
description: A simple split rail fence overgrown with climbing pink rose vines borders the walkway.  Through a break in the fence a glimpse of well-manicured grass dotted with picnic tables and shade trees can be seen.  Nodding in the slight breeze, the heavy pink roses perfume the air with their sweet scent.
